'''天主教聖路易斯教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Sancti Ludovici in Argentina}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de San Luis}}）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教庫約的聖胡安總教區|庫約的聖胡安總教區]]。

教區於1934年4月20日成立。<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=II |year=1935 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=257-263 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425134719/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-25 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>位於[[聖路易斯省|聖路易斯省]]，2010年時有365,000名教友（佔轄區總人口94.8%）、47個[[堂區|堂區]]和74名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-es|加俾額爾·伯爾納鐸·巴爾巴|Gabriel Bernardo Barba}}<ref name="Vatican20200609">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 09.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/09/200609a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609180844/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/09/200609a.html |archivedate=2020-06-09 |language=en |date=2020-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|喬治·類斯·洛納|Jorge Luis Lona}}和{{link-es|伯多祿·但尼爾·馬丁內斯-佩雷阿|Pedro Daniel Martinez Perea}}<ref name="Vatican20200609" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE (CONTINUAZIONE), 22.02.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/02/22/0111/00265.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609212510/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/02/22/0111/00265.html |archivedate=2020-06-09 |date=2011-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

